# 💬 ChatNav

ChatNav is a modern chat application that combines messaging, notes, and task management into a single interface with a simple and interactive user experience.

---

## 🚀 Features

### Splash Screen
- Animated loading screen
- Smooth app transition

### Chats
- Open and close chat
- Contact search
- Send messages
- Chat rendering
- Emoji support
- Search messages
- Starred messages
- Forward messages

### Notes
- Add notes
- Edit notes
- Delete notes
- Search notes

### Todo
- Add tasks
- Add reminder date and time
- Separate Pending and Completed tasks

### Media & Files
- File upload
- Media viewer

### Voice
- Voice recording interface

---

